            <title>[DATAMONGO-829] NearQuery, when used in conjunction with a Query, it sets num=0, unless Query specifies otherwise</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAMONGO-829</link>
                <project id="10701" key="DATAMONGO">Spring Data MongoDB</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;/p&gt;

